token_info.description: “Teach Kids to Code” was a series of posters originally created with Scriptographer in 2012 by Amelie Maia and Christina Winkless.  These drawings have been updated as interactive NFT's for #OBJKT4OBJKT swap weekend.  Code available at: github.com/ameliemaia/teach-kids-to-code
